library("limma")
vGene <- voom(dge, mod, plot = TRUE)

eb_results <- eBayes(lmFit(vGene))

de_results <- topTable(
    eb_results,
    coef = 2,
    number = nrow(rse_gene_SRP132816),
    sort.by = "none"
)
